an class="ls0">”<span class="_ _8"></span> </span></span></div><div class="t m0 x23 h4 yd9 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">既然机会如此难得，<span class="_ _5"></span>你们在学佛的过程中，<span class="_ _4"></span>一方面要总</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yd6 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">体上修学佛法，<span class="_ _4"></span>同时，<span class="_ _6"></span>尤其要修学菩提心和空性。<span class="_ _4"></span>若能在寺</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yb7 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">院的上师、<span class="_ _4"></span>格西面前，<span class="_ _6"></span>首先听闻一些这方面的教义，<span class="_ _4"></span>之后通</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yb8 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">达其中的内容，并对别人进行引导，这才是最有意义的。 </div><div class="t m0 x23 h4 yd7 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">一般来讲，藏族人从小就对三宝很有信心，可是如今，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5b ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">许多年轻人、<span class="_ _4"></span>尤其是学生，<span class="_ _6"></span>在这方面却比较差。<span class="_ _4"></span>像你们青海</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
